      {
        "segment": "The answer to this question probably has to do with our distorted view of time.",
        "start_offset": 24,
        "end_offset": 98,
        "start": 1.92,
        "end": 7.84
      },
      {
        "segment": "But I see wanderers in this density who have come fifth or sixth density.",
        "start_offset": 116,
        "end_offset": 246,
        "start": 9.28,
        "end": 19.68
      },
      {
        "segment": "Seems to me should already be in a relatively high degree of adeptness who must follow a slightly or somewhat different path back to the adeptness that they once they previously had in the higher density and get as close to it as they can in third density.",
        "start_offset": 258,
        "end_offset": 596,
        "start": 20.64,
        "end": 47.68
      },
      {
        "segment": "Is this correct?",
        "start_offset": 609,
        "end_offset": 628,
        "start": 48.72,
        "end": 50.24
      },
      {
        "segment": "Hi, M R.",
        "start_offset": 672,
