        "end_offset": 891,
        "start": 62.160000000000004,
        "end": 71.28
      },
      {
        "segment": "We shall address the subject in general.",
        "start_offset": 909,
        "end_offset": 1013,
        "start": 72.72,
        "end": 81.04
      },
      {
        "segment": "There are many wanderers whom you may call adepts who do know conscious work in the present incarnation.",
        "start_offset": 1049,
        "end_offset": 1473,
        "start": 83.92,
        "end": 117.84
      },
      {
        "segment": "But if the eye is not turned as this sphere is tossed, then perchance it will pass the entity by if it turned its eyes upon the sphere catching would be easy.",
        "start_offset": 1976,
        "end_offset": 2640,
        "start": 158.08,
        "end": 211.20000000000002
      },
      {
        "segment": "In the case of wanderers, which seek to recapitulate the degree of adeptness, which each had acquired previous to this life experience, we may note that even after the forgetting process has been penetrated.",
        "start_offset": 2686,
        "end_offset": 3399,
        "start": 214.88,
        "end": 271.92
      },
      {
